sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as ProjectDetailPage / AIInsightsPanel
    participant Q as useProjectStats (TanStack Query)
    participant AX as Axios apiClient
    participant API as Express + ProjectController.getStats
    participant UC as GetProjectStatsUseCase
    participant TR as TaskRepository (Prisma)
    participant AIP as AIProvider port
    participant OAI as OpenAI API

    User->>UI: Open project detail
    UI->>Q: useProjectStats(projectId)
    Q->>AX: GET /api/v1/projects/:id/stats
    AX->>API: HTTP request
    API->>UC: execute({ projectId })
    UC->>TR: count + status/priority distribution + overdue
    TR-->>UC: metrics
    UC->>AIP: generateProjectInsights(context)
    alt OPENAI_API_KEY set -> OpenAIProvider
        AIP->>OAI: chat.completions (gpt-4o-mini, json_object)
        OAI-->>AIP: JSON { summary, recommendations }
    else default -> MockAIProvider
        AIP->>AIP: build deterministic insights
    end
    AIP-->>UC: AIInsights (summary, recommendations, generatedAt)
    Note over UC: try/catch — on failure aiInsights = null
    UC-->>API: ProjectStatsOutput (+ aiInsights)
    API->>API: mapProjectStats -> { data: { ..., ai_insights } }
    API-->>AX: 200 JSON
    AX-->>Q: ProjectStats
    Q-->>UI: Render summary + recommendations (or empty/error state)
